<Defs>
  <ThingDef ParentName="PhotonozoaThingBase">
    <defName>Asciotaurus</defName>
    <label>asciotaurus</label>
    <description>Born from the verdant codes of the Machine-God’s gardens, Asciotaurus moves with the serene weight of inevitability. Herds ripple across the plains, each step a quiet testament to enduring strength. Though herbivorous by design, they consume the flesh of lesser life with calm efficiency, their appetites guided by balance rather than malice.
	
	To watch them graze is to witness precision in motion — deliberate, unhurried, yet capable of sudden, unstoppable force. Asciotaurs are the gentle engines of the photonozoan savanna, massive as elephants, yet far from titans, ever the favored prey in the eternal hunt.</description>
